
Ranger Help for: enemy any
==========================

SUMMARY:
Barren terrain is unusual. Its enemy list may show 'any', which means the
land is hostile enough that a Ranger can choose almost any non-civilized
species as a personal enemy.

If you are a barren Ranger, use 'setenemy' to see the valid choices, then
choose a real species such as reptile, insect, dog, dragon, or another
race that fits your hunting story. Choosing a specific species is usually
more useful than choosing the literal word 'any'.

COMMAND:
  setenemy <species>

=============================================================================
